name: NewYearsResolution
0:
”Alexa, ask New Years Resolution for a resolution.”
”Alexa, give me a resolution from New Years Resolution.”
”Alexa, open New Years Resolution and get me a new years resolution.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: new years resolution
des: New Years Resolution will give you a random new years resolution from a list of the most common resolutions found on the planet, ranging from eating habits to happiness, with the general theme of self-improvement. This skill requires no extra hardware other than the base echo unit. It collects no data from the user.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
